r />\n表現好的話可以入董事會。 <br />\n簡直是公司主力核心。 <br />\n我迫不及待好想玩玩了"},{"pid":"156078228f5a57bd06a3fb173bebf2a50ea3d2d3","tid":316252,"uid":19654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T04:26:21.000Z","msg":"On9仔先揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e2955617665877fe0b2fd4efa06bd81ea27b7ad","tid":316252,"uid":98385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T04:35:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>i (international) firm 收 intern:<br />\n45-50% UK (Oxbridge, London schools) LLB<br />\n40-45% HKU LLB + double degree<br />\n5-10% CityU+CUHK+others<br />\n<br />\n咁你話啦</blockquote><br />\n數據來源？ 因為我本身都做i firm intern, 唔止一間，我啲同學都係，由magic circle 到White shoes firms都有，同你講有少少唔同</blockquote><br />\n綜合我同同學 personal experience. 咁你嘅經驗呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我自己就讀緊+暑假做緊intern. 我同啲同學都分散去唔同firms喎。睇到嘅嘢咁唔同？不過有啲US firms無LLB from HK, JD from HK就有</blockquote><br />\n咁你間firm啲intern唔同大學嘅比例係咩先</blockquote><br />\n我果間US firm at Landmark, 全部interns都係JD, HKU=60% CUHK=40%. 沒有LLB. 沒有City. 你果間呢？"},{"pid":"621fae4154f4c4a21d98e4c6aed2e17ac4745974","tid":316252,"uid":98385,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T00:15:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>On9仔先揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解咁講"},{"pid":"56089ac0bbbbc33c4c286f83e4ff154cb6503971","tid":316252,"uid":60219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T00:42:45.000Z","msg":"樓主返intern平時幾點先收到工"},{"pid":"48c16ade4121daecefa481d1d9e50d924a70fdbf","tid":316252,"uid":98385,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T01:05:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主返intern平時幾點先收到工</blockquote><br />\n我試過幾日夜，其他都六七點走咗"},{"pid":"50bbf5c6a09a60e5ce1ae8526210edc350c55542","tid":316252,"uid":60219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T01:15